file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: apim-todo
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /todo:
    post:
      summary: CreateTodo
      operationId: createtodo
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 
    get:
      summary: GetTodos
      operationId: gettodos
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 
  '/todo/{id}':
    get:
      summary: GetTodoById
      operationId: gettodobyid
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: ''
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 
    put:
      summary: UpdateTodo
      operationId: updatetodo
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: ''
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 
    delete:
      summary: DeleteTodo
      operationId: deletetodo
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: ''
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 
components:
  schemas:
    Todo:
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        taskDescription:
          type: string
        isCompleted:
          type: bool
    Todos:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/Todo"
    Error:
      required:
        - code
        - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
